net.jawr.web.resource.bundle.variant
Interface VariantResolver

All Known Implementing Classes:
BrowserResolver, ConnectionTypeResolver, CssSkinVariantResolver, LocaleVariantResolverWrapper
public interface VariantResolver

The variant request resolver determines from the HttpServletRequest what is the variant bundle to send to the user.
